{"word":"G3911 - παραφέρω - paraphérō - par-af-er'-o - Remove","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">παραφέρω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">paraphérō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">par-af-er'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Remove</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - நீக்கு"},{"paragraph":"1. to bear bring to, put before"},{"paragraph":"2. to lead aside"},{"paragraph":"3. to carry past, lead past"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G3844 - παρά - pará - par-ah'/3844\">G3844</a> and <a href=\"#/G5342 - φέρω - phérō - fer'-o/5342\">G5342</a> (including its alternate forms); to <i>bear along</i> or <i>aside</i>, that is, <i>carry off</i> (literally or figuratively); by implication to <i>avert:</i> - remove, take away.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}